        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/62.400549498728566_10.538986154828823"/>
        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/0"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Exogenous. The innovation is associated with the Rorosmat brand as it promotes and sells the regional products. Apart from the e-commerce of Rorosmat, the mill also has its own website where everyone can make an order. The innovation is related to New marketing strategies. The land use systems involved are Cropland. The local assets include Natural, social and cultural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


